[25/12/2017 06:57:41] <font color="#ffffff">El conflicto colombiano es</font>
[25/12/2017 06:57:41] <font color="#ffffff">un conflicto</font>
[25/12/2017 06:57:44] <font color="#ffffff">que se ha desarrollado</font>
